    "Data availability • Absence of historical data about soil condition, crop growth, weather, and other relevant parameters.",
    "• Data scarcity and insufficient centralized data.",
    "• Incomplete data could result in flawed insights.",
    "• Encouraging data recording according to established standards and protocols.",
    "• Incomplete data should be improved by techniques like data synthesis and imputation to avoid flawed AI-decisions."
  ]
